                           continued Oct. 1892, p. 637, part of a two-part article (Part I pp.
                           433-499; Part II pp. 637-710). <ref
                              target="https://bahai-library.com/browne_catalogue_manuscripts_two"
                              >page 665.</ref> The new class mark and additional information from
                              <ref target="https://cudl.lib.cam.ac.uk/view/PR-A-00233-00004/1">R. A.
                              Nicholson: <hi rend="italic">A descriptive catalogue of the Oriental
                                 MSS belonging to the late E.G. Browne</hi>. Cambridge,
                           1932</ref>.</source>
                     </recordHist>
